Salient Features of Quarkchain
•	Unlike other coin, Quarkchain is based on POS. Which would make the network  thousand times faster and energy efficient.
•	Its Architecture is based on Sharding, 
•	Utility – Social Media, HFT,IOT, Gaming and Payment

Quarkchain is permissionless block chain. It is secure, scalable,decentalised blockchain. Its central technology is Sharding.
